{"version":1,"entries":{"person_96634_translations":{"at":1774726985891,"data":{"id":96634,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Lee Han-wi (born June 17, 1961) is a South Korean actor. Since his acting debut in 1983, Lee has become a prolific supporting actor on Korean film and television. He is particularly known for his mastery of ad-libbing.","name":"Lee Han-wi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이한위","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"23岁时报名参加KBS第十期演艺人才培训班而出道的李韩威是一位在大屏幕和电视剧场中都享有高人气的实力派中坚演员，2005至06年期间他接连拍摄了《激流勇退》、《外出》、《我爱你，莫顺》、《野兽》、《伟大的家谱》等十多部电影，其中不乏反响强烈的优秀作品，演技出众的他发挥异常稳定，身价也随之暴增。此外李韩威出演的电视剧包括《19岁的纯情》、《雪的女王》、《露露公主》、《再见武器》、《复活》以及《蓝色生死恋》等等。","name":"李汉威","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lee Han-wi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"23 歲時報名參加 KBS 第十期演藝人才培訓班而出道的李韓威是一位在大屏幕和電視劇場中都享有高人氣的實力派中堅演員，2005 至 06 年期間他接聯拍攝了《激流勇退》、《外出》、《我愛你，莫順》、《超時空愛殺》、《偉大的家譜》等十多部電影，其中不乏反響強烈的優秀作品，演技出眾的他發揮異常穩定，身價也隨之暴增。此外李韓威出演的電視劇包括《19 歲的純情》、《雪的女王》、《露露公主》、《再見武器》、《復活》以及《藍色生死戀》等等。","name":"李漢威","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Лі Хан Ві","primary":false}}]}},"person_6321_translations":{"at":1774726991881,"data":{"id":6321,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Valente Rodriguez was born on 14 February 1961 in Edcouch, Texas, USA. He is an actor and producer, known for McFarland, USA (2015)